abstract: Stock prices recover after previous day's drop amid interest rate uncertainty; technology and banking shares lift market near end of day.
lead_paragraph: Shares of Volkswagen were slumping after revelations that the automaker rigged emissions tests in the United States.

headline.main: Market Mostly Up a Day After a Sell-Off
headline.print_headline: Shares Rise, Recovering Partly From Sell-Off Over Rates
